    "smartwatches) exchange information about the past and present states of their owner with health apps.",
    "Similar to human-to-robot memory communication, the growing prominence of the robot-to-robot model is attributed to the post-scarcity of the current memory ecosystem.",
    "The unprecedented volume of memory-related content causes the necessity to rely on robotic agents both to help users navigate available information (i.e.",
